  EffectDiscription_ENG: 'Digivolve: 1 from [Belphemon: Rage Mode][On Play][When
    Digivolving] By placing 1 [Belphemon: Rage Mode] from your trash as this Digimon''s
    top digivolution card, until the end of your opponent''s turn, this Digimon can''t
    attack and isn''t affected by your opponent''s effects. [Opponent''s Turn][Once
    Per Turn] When an opponent''s Digimon attacks, by trashing 2 cards in your hand,
    end the attack.'
